Micro Core accepts the following additional boot time options:

 microcore {cron|syslog}              Start various daemons at boot
 microcore host=xxxx                  Set hostname to xxxx
 microcore secure                     Set password
 microcore protect                    Password Encrypted Backup
 microcore noautologin                Skip automatic login
 microcore tz=GMT+8                   Timezone tz=PST+8PDT,M3.2.0/2,M11.1.0/2
 microcore user=abc                   Specify alternate user
 microcore desktop=yyy                Specify alternate window manager
 microcore laptop                     Force load laptop related modules
 microcore embed                      Stay on initramfs
 microcore nozswap                    Skip compressed swap in ram
 microcore xvesa=800x600x32           Set Xvesa default screen resolution
 microcore bkg=image.{jpg|png|gif}    Set background from /opt/backgrounds
 microcore blacklist=ssb              Blacklist a single module
 microcore multivt                    Allows for multiple virtual terminals
 
